
PointList instruction
---------------------

The ``PointList`` instruction can be used to create an array of named points.
The typical use is:

.. code-block:: Box

  pl = PointList["name1", point1, "name2", point2, ...]

The name comes just before the point it refers to and is optional.
The points can be retrieved from ``pl`` by using the ``Get`` method.
